Jim True-Frost https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jim_True-Frost 0 Jim True-Frost (born July 31, 1966), born Jim True, is an American stage, television and screen actor. He is most known for his portrayal of Roland "Prez" Pryzbylewski on all five seasons of the HBO program The Wire.
